019
020import static org.apiguardian.api.API.Status.STABLE;
021
022import org.apiguardian.api.API;
023import org.tquadrat.foundation.annotation.ClassVersion;
024import org.tquadrat.foundation.svg.type.SVGNumber;
025
026/**
027 *  The definition for the SVG {@code <marker>} element when used as a
028 *  positioned marker.
029 *
030 *  @extauthor Thomas Thrien - thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org
031 *  @version $Id: SVGPositionedMarker.java 980 2022-01-06 15:29:19Z tquadrat $
032 *  @since 0.0.5
033 *
034 *  @UMLGraph.link
035 */
036@ClassVersion( sourceVersion = "$Id: SVGPositionedMarker.java 980 2022-01-06 15:29:19Z tquadrat $" )
037@API( status = STABLE, since = "0.0.5" )
038public sealed interface SVGPositionedMarker extends SVGMarker permits SVGElementAdapter, org.tquadrat.foundation.svg.internal.SVGPositionedMarkerImpl
039{
040        /*---------*\
041    ====** Methods **==========================================================
042        \*---------*/
043    /**
044     *  Sets the relative position for this marker.
045     *
046     *  @param  value   The distance.
047     */
048    public void setPosition( final SVGNumber value );
049}
